text: High-end stuff, ultra friendly. Both Swee and Ryan are very hospitable to be with. Great experience!

I emailed this store for some advice on a woofer repair I needed, but zero reply for 6 days.

A simple "cannot do" reply might have been courteous, but nada, zilch.
Good customer service and very honest salesmamship. Not many these days. Have gotten quite a few number of products from them.
